window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b><i>They're brilliant surgeons with stethoscopes and six-pack abs, but beneath those arrogant smirks, these men are hiding hearts encased in ice. Haunted by past tragedies, they've sworn off love, convinced they're better off alone. </i></b><br> <br> Get ready for sparks to fly as witty banter leads to smoldering chemistry, and these guarded surgeons find themselves falling for the women who dare to mend their broken hearts.<br> <br> This collection will leave you breathless and believing that even the coldest hearts can be thawed by the power of love.</p>"; 
